{"word":"ἀδόκητος","slug":"ἀδόκητος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀδόκητος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δοκέω'><el>δοκέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>unexpected</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>τὸ ἀδ.</el> <i>the unexpectedness</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-τως</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; so <el>ἀδόκητα</el> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <el>ἀπὸ τοῦ ἀδοκήτου</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}